夏薩特，去要今場的門票。』我覺得事件不太尋常，立刻拿出電話，上google，再打『費蘭尼兄弟』，發現兩個人幾乎一模一樣。我給門僮看一看，問他今早來的是誰。他指出的原來那人是費蘭尼的弟弟。」</blockquote><br />\n咁細佬又無講大話"},{"pid":"6cd322c1c6609d2418d7b053fd70b9ede2406706","tid":216484,"uid":30182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T09:12:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>曼聯應該簽晒兩個, 再簽埋普巴三兄弟</blockquote><br />\n再簽返大孖細孖</blockquote><br />\n搵埋迪保亞兄弟教 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81fbbd9e5fc2cbe1f4b87efb3681e0ccb9a7a569","tid":216484,"uid":21222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T09:14:41.000Z","msg":"咁似樣好心就唔好一齊爆炸頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6dc1ece43a6300d0ad1ff9ddfb374ce1977d704","tid":216484,"uid":40461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T09:38:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4WKt4pN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4WKt4pN.jpg&h=319b4d99&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"00e41331b1a7ffd04678311f59876e0731c14ae3","tid":216484,"uid":50385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T09:41:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>曼聯應該簽晒兩個, 再簽埋普巴三兄弟</blockquote><br />\n再簽返大孖細孖</blockquote><br />\n搵埋迪保亞兄弟教 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n再叫尼維利兄弟復出"},{"pid":"0ca9226323b9cf4f6885682eacdf52754e19619b","tid":216484,"uid":57227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T09:42:02.000Z","msg":"細佬個鼻大D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19b0c1dfd3f22737d00dd932103df738c42f369a","tid":216484,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T09:42:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>曼聯應該簽晒兩個, 再簽埋普巴三兄弟</blockquote><br />\n再簽返大孖細孖</blockquote><br />\n搵埋迪保亞兄弟教 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquo